# Decap CMS uploads land here.
#
# Decap's `media_folder: public/marketing/uploads` in
# public/cms/config.yml needs this directory to exist in the repo
# before Decap probes it on startup (otherwise the GitHub Contents
# API returns 404 and clutters the console).
#
# Files uploaded via the CMS will be committed alongside this
# .gitkeep. Safe to delete this file once there's at least one
# real upload here.
